title: Lottery Manager 2008
description:
Lottery Manager 2008 helps keep you organized, plus it also includes advanced filters and wheels designed to help lottery players get the best bang for their buck.


Easy to use
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Playing the lottery doesn&#039;t have to be costly and complicated. Ultimate
Lottery Manager is easy to use and learn. Our software makes it easy
for you to search tickets to see if you have a winning ticket.

Save time and money
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Forget wasting time using a pencil and
paper to pick your numbers. Our product makes playing the lottery as
quick as pointing and clicking. Lottery filters may save you money by
eliminating unlikely combination&#039;s.

Extensible
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Developers can take advantage of the extensible
architecture and add new features. New games, wheels, statistics, and
filters can be added by installing additional plug-ins.

Features

    * Search past drawings
    * Full, Abbreviated, and Key Wheels
    * Drawing Summary Statistics
    * Repeating Numbers Search
    * Number Filtering
    * Free Program Updates
    * And much more...
